							<h4 class="policies_heading sub_heading">NO PURCHASE OR PAYMENT OF ANY KIND NECESSARY TO ENTER. PURCHASING WILL NOT IMPROVE YOUR CHANCES OF WINNING</h4>

							<p>By submitting an entry, you agree to these official rules:</p>


							<h4 class="policies_heading">01. Eligibility</h4>
							<p>This Contest is Sponsored by Discovered USA, Inc. (Discovered) (and other Sponsor(s)s TBD). Contest is open to residents of the U.S. including Puerto Rico, territories and possessions, and Canada, who are 18 years of age or older at the time of entry. Employees of Discovered, or its affiliated or subsidiary companies, and their immediate family members, are not eligible to enter the Contest. Contest is governed by the laws of the USA. All federal, state and local laws and regulations apply. Void where prohibited by law. All times referred to in these official rules are based on Eastern Time. Discovered is the official timekeeper for this contest.</p>

							<h4 class="policies_heading">02. To Enter</h4>
							<p>Entry begins at 12:00 PM Eastern time. on 9/1/2021, and ends at 11:59 p.m. on 10/31/2021 at 12:00 PM Eastern time. To enter visit <a href="<?=base_url('giveaways');?>" class="policies_link" target="_blank">www.discovered.tv/giveaways</a>  and follow the instructions. All entries must include your full name, address, city, state, zip code and email address. All entrants must follow Discovered <a href="https://www.instagram.com/discoveredglobal/" class="policies_link" target="_blank">@discovered_usa</a> on Instagram.  Entries submitted in geographic areas in which the entry is not permissible will be disqualified. If entries do not contain all necessary information, entrant will be disqualified. If the entrant fails to follow Discovered on Instagram, they will be disqualified.   Please be certain to follow all directions. Please do not submit multiple entries. In the event that two similar entries are received, only 1 entry will be included in the final contest.</p>

							<h4 class="policies_heading">03. As an option you may submit your original video in MP4 or MOV format to your account as an Emerging Creator. </h4>
							<p>The entry must not be lewd, obscene, sexually explicit, pornographic, disparaging, defamatory, libelous, or otherwise inappropriate or objectionable, as determined by the Judges and/or Discovered and Sponsor(s) in their sole and absolute discretion. Discovered and Sponsor(s) and Discovered reserves the right to disqualify any entry deemed inappropriate. The entry must not infringe the copyright, trademark, privacy, publicity or other intellectual property rights of any person or entity. Entries submitted in geographic areas in which the entry is not permissible will be disqualified. All entries remain the property of the entrant however, Discovered has the right to use all entries in all print and electronic media, and to edit them for brevity and clarity. </p>

							<h4 class="policies_heading">04. Judging:</h4>
							<p> <span class="policies_link">Judges from Discovered will select the best videos based on originality as determined by the Judges.</span> All entries will be judged using the criteria stated above. Judge's decisions are final. </p>


							<h4 class="policies_heading">05. Prize(s)</h4>
							<p>One grand-prize winner will receive $500 and his/her video will be published on Discovered Music Home Page for a minimum of 1 week. Discovered will also select five (5) runner-up winners to receive $100. All taxes, if any, as a result of winning this contest are each winner/finalist’s responsibility. Discovered will not be responsible for any loss, liability or damage arising out of a winner/finalist’s acceptance or use of the prize. All Prizes are guaranteed to be awarded provided a sufficient number of entries are received.</p>

