il addresses for the domain associated with the submitted email address. Discovered and Sponsor(s), in their sole discretion, reserve the right to disqualify any person tampering with the operation of the website or the entry process and/or any entry that it determines, in its sole discretion does not meet the requirements of the official Rules. All prizes will be awarded. </p>

							<p>Winners and finalists will be notified by email within two months of the closing date. All winners and finalists will be required to agree to the use of their name and likeness and entry for promotional purposes (except where prohibited by law). Each winner and finalist may be required to execute a Statement of Eligibility and Release and Payment Authorization within 30 days of prize notification attempt or (s)he may be disqualified and prize may be awarded to an alternate winner. Return of prize or prize notification as undeliverable will result in disqualification and an alternate winner/finalist may be selected. Entry and/or acceptance of prize(s) constitutes permission for Discovered and Sponsor(s) and their agencies (if any) to use the winners’ name, address (city and state) and/or likeness for advertising and trade purposes without further compensation or authorization, worldwide and in perpetuity, in any and all forms of media, now known and hereafter devised, unless prohibited by law.</p>

